{"tid":902193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[麻煩大家入一入黎]pt model假結婚陷阱","createTime":"2018-11-14T15:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T15:31:06.000Z","uid":211906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f387cd723f624223cd94119844463ac2c2b881d","tid":902193,"uid":211906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友有個冇聯絡十年既同學突然搵番佢<br />\n我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 有job介紹俾你 即日出糧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：要做咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : pt model <br />\n之後就打電話俾我朋友 大致內容 $600-1000/hour 影3、4個鐘 唔洗睇樣唔睇身材高矮肥瘦會p圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有冇ig/fb page睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：冇，係私人攝影師，為興趣拍野<br />\n<br />\n去到約定當日，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出現之後尻噏左幾句會影d咩 就問有冇回鄉證 話番大陸或者澳門影會再高啲人工 <br />\n<br />\n之後有個男人黎左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就以為係攝影師。個男人一坐低講既野就開始奇奇怪怪。 話要拎錢就要番大陸簽啲野、通常抽5%佣金、做model 時薪先得個幾百蚊 跟我地番去簽個名就幾萬蚊、上一上大陸簽左文件 做場戲 就即刻有3-4萬收、想要錢既話可以即刻去律師樓整張單身證明 然後番去廣洲簽啲文件就搞掂。係咁遊說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟佢地番大陸做假結婚<br />\n<br />\n騙徒FB：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/14/mJdiTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2FmJdiTG.png&h=ea308b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請人post<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/14/kyQbct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2FkyQbct.png&h=c9ad5525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/14/OTUqym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2FOTUqym.png&h=1aae05d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手傳出去 想借我地香港人過橋，幫啲大陸人黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋警告下身邊啲朋友，男男女女都好，唔好中伏，今次就話係假結婚，下次唔知開邊樣，唔係次次都咁好彩可以話走就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ec795d3fdff611fcb39375a54479d14741b242","tid":902193,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce57e26e344c1c8e26effaf7cb47f070ddd69b1","tid":902193,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"嘩真係要廣傳"}]}